          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The experimental  setap  described  and  results  are",
                " presented   of   the  measurements  of  the  angular",
                " dependence of the SIGMAp,n(theta)-asymmetry  of  the",
                " cross  sections  4He(g,p)T and 4He(g,n)3He reactions",
                " induced by linearly polarized photons with  energies",
                " Eg   =  40,  60  and  80  MeV.  The  SIGMAp,n(theta)",
                " calculated  in  the   relativistic   gauge-invariant",
                " approach  are  in  satisfactory  agreement  with the",
                " experimental  data,  with  the  exception   of   the",
                " asymmetry   of  the  cross  sections  of  the  (g,n)",
                " reaction at Eg = 60 MeV and theta = 90 - 120 degree,",
                " where  the  theoretical  values are close to 1,  but",
                " experimental SIGMA,n(theta) = 0.47 (0.18)."
              ]
            }
          ],
